// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-0899 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: fa5f8522-361a-56c0-a0ca-9a16e94d0fb5

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *debian:11* OR ImageFileName = *debian:12* OR ImageFileName = *debian:13* OR ImageFileName = *debian:14* OR ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:6*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
